{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.600", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.240", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.880", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.320", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zun\u00e4chst: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.000", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist ausgesprochen erfreulich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.600", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie sich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.960", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine sehr geehrten Damen und Herren von der Linken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.520", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einem Zweig der Alterssicherung zuwenden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.760", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der vor allem die Eigenverantwortung der B\u00fcrger betrifft; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.600", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn mit der Kritik, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.440", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in Ihrem Antrag steckt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.560", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben Sie durchaus recht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.240", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man kann es den B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrgern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.600", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in eigener Verantwortung ihre Altersvorsorge durch Verzicht und Sparsamkeit verbessern wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.960", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ganz einfach nicht vermitteln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.760", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ihre Krankenkassenbeitr\u00e4ge doppelt berechnet werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.480", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aus einem ganz \u00e4hnlichen Grund hat die FDP-Fraktion im Deutschen Bundestag dem Gesetz zur Modernisierung der gesetzlichen Krankenversicherung im Jahr\u00a02003 nicht zugestimmt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.800", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damals \u00fcbrigens als einzige Fraktion."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.960", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.360", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da hatten Sie eine au\u00dferparlamentarische Bildungspause, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.600", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir zuletzt eingelegt haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.560", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir Freie Demokraten kritisieren seit langer Zeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.040", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es in vielen Versicherungsvertr\u00e4gen zu einer doppelten Beitragsbelastung kommen kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.720", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das verletzt das Gerechtigkeitsempfinden vieler B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.160", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie f\u00fchlen sich vom Staat get\u00e4uscht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.720", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um es diplomatisch zu sagen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.560", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zumal von der Doppelbelastung auch Vertr\u00e4ge betroffen sein k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.280", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die vor der gesetzlichen Regelung abgeschlossen wurden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.240", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die B\u00fcrger k\u00f6nnen ihre Altersvorsorge nicht immer dann umkrempeln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.880", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn der Gesetzgeber wieder neue Regelungen schafft."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.560", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man kann die Auffassung vertreten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.880", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass in so einem Fall auch der Vertrauensschutz verletzt wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.560", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der auf Artikel\u00a020 Absatz\u00a03 des Grundgesetzes zur\u00fcckgeht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.960", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der bisher vorliegende Beschluss des Bundesverfassungsgerichts aus dem Jahr\u00a02010 kommt zwar zu einem formal sicherlich richtigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.720", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber in den Augen vieler B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger nicht befriedigenden Schluss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.600", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Gesetzgeber sollte von den Grundregeln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.480", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die er f\u00fcr die Steuerpflicht seiner B\u00fcrger definiert hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.280", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch bei Abgaben und Versicherungen nicht wesentlich abweichen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.320", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Menschen verstehen es nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.160", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass hier mit zweierlei Ma\u00df gemessen wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.560", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.400", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "lieber Kollege Henke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.680", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kommen wir trotz \u00e4hnlicher Gedanken zu ganz anderen Schl\u00fcssen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.600", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn ich bin der Auffassung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.600", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass bei der Bemessung der Beitr\u00e4ge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.320", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ausdr\u00fccklich nicht versicherungsmathematisch erfolgt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.880", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern nach dem Leistungsf\u00e4higkeitsprinzip dem Steuerrecht entlehnt ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.680", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Grunds\u00e4tze des Steuerrechtes angewendet werden sollten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.120", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir d\u00fcrfen das anders machen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.640", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber wir k\u00f6nnen es den B\u00fcrgern so halt nicht erkl\u00e4ren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.160", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich wei\u00df nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.720", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Sie den Beschluss des Bundesverfassungsgerichts lesen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.920", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich lese ihn so: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.600", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "H\u00e4tte es sich um eine Steuer gehandelt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.320", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00e4re der Beschluss m\u00f6glicherweise anders ausgefallen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.280", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihr Ansatz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.200", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich in dieser speziellen Frage der Krankenversicherung an den wohldefinierten Grunds\u00e4tzen des Steuerrechts zu orientieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.240", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "begr\u00fc\u00dfen wir als Freie Demokraten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.160", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber so erfreulich dieser Ansatz auch ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.600", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so verfehlen Sie bei den L\u00f6sungsvorschl\u00e4gen am Ende doch das eigentliche Ziel. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.920", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihr Ansatz geht n\u00e4mlich in einem Punkt nicht weit genug: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.440", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die doppelte Belastung bei den monatlich entrichteten Beitr\u00e4gen haben Sie richtig erkannt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.000", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber f\u00fcr das gleiche Problem bei der Entgeltumwandlung aus Sonderzahlungen legen Sie keine L\u00f6sung vor."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.440", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei dem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.280", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was Sie stattdessen anbieten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.960", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schie\u00dfen Sie zum anderen weit \u00fcber das Ziel hinaus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.440", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie nehmen an, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.960", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass eine Ausweitung der staatlichen Vorsorge das Problem l\u00f6sen w\u00fcrde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.360", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Wirklichkeit \u00fcberspannen Sie das Thema damit aber und stellen sich einer wirklich geeigneten L\u00f6sung in den Weg."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.760", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Etwas am\u00fcsiert hat mich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.680", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich zitiere aus Ihrem Antrag\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.280", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Hinweis auf die hier festgestellte \u201ekalte Enteignung\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.000", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daran werden wir Sie gerne das n\u00e4chste Mal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.720", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie mit w\u00e4rmeren und mitunter richtig hei\u00dfen Enteignungsfantasien kommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.520", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "erinnern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.760", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.160", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es w\u00e4re in der Tat gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.880", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr den in diesem Gesetz erkannten Missstand auch eine sinnvolle Abhilfe zu erarbeiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.000", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daher w\u00e4re dieser Antrag in einem zust\u00e4ndigen Ausschuss sehr gut aufgehoben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.480", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch wir pl\u00e4dieren daher f\u00fcr eine \u00dcberweisung an den Ausschuss f\u00fcr Arbeit und Soziales."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.800", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00e4chste Rednerin: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.000", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr die Fraktion B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen die Kollegin Maria Klein-Schmeink."
   ]
  }
 ]
}